snippet.title: Disassembly VR: Trailer 2a
snippet.description:
Announcing Disassembly VR: Ultimate Reality Destruction! Available now for the HTC Vive and Oculus Rift. With awesome new tools and weapons, experience destruction like never before!

Same as Trailer 2 but showing some disassembly and shooting the computer and TV. (Reupload because original was stuck in 360p)

Steam link:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/973700/Disassembly_VR/

Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/Vt8Exh3
